"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777742","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-10-30","<p>In replying to this question, I have assumed that the hon. Member is referring to the Type 23 Frigates. I refer the hon. Member to the answer given by my predecessor the former Minister of State for Defence Procurement (Mr Philip Dunne) on 1 March 2016 to Question 28004 to the hon. Member for Islington South and Finsbury (Emily Thornberry).</p><p> </p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin",,"2017-10-30T16:21:02.417Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777742/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777742/answer","20160301_28004_Type_23_Frigates.docx","20160301_28004_Type_23_Frigates.docx","28004 - WQnA extract on Type 23 Frigates","28004 - WQnA extract on Type 23 Frigates","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/777742/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-10-25","Type 26 Frigates","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the retirement dates are of each of the 13 Type 26 frigates.","false","Biography information for Luke Pollard","Plymouth, Sutton and Devonport","Luke Pollard","109635"
